rComments: His lectures were not at all necessary to do well in the class.  The only reason to attend was the quick quizzes he gave as an attendance grade basically.  If I didn't blow off lecture constantly I would have gotten an A instead of a B+.  Besides that, he's a very likeable guy and I LOVE HADI!!!
He was pretty hard to understand and lectures did NOT relate to test!!
Only thing I didn't like was that there were pop quizzes almost every day in lecture - but they are open note and you can talk to classmates --> easy!  It just makes lecture pretty much mandatory...

quite an easy class. he does have a mini quiz everyday so you have to go to class. the midterm was the easiest thing ever!!! overall pretty good but he does speak about his home country a little too much.
Hadi is so awesome. The class is actually really interesting to go to and he explains everything very well. Mid-term and final are easy. Go to class, you'll understand!

He's so cute! and a great professor!

I love Hadi! Take this class. Now.
